Place your trained .h5 model files here.

Expected filenames (in priority order):
  skin_disease_model_transfer_best.h5   ← best checkpoint from transfer learning
  skin_disease_model_transfer.h5        ← final transfer learning model
  skin_disease_model_best.h5            ← best checkpoint from scratch training
  skin_disease_model.h5                 ← final scratch model

Train a model by running:
  cd ../
  python train_model.py
